INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3412597742, 'officer_ability_desc_51006', '<color=#309BBF>Adapt and Assimilate</color>
At the start of each round, if opponents Hull health is below 95%, Dezoc has <color=#40FF60>{0:#,#%}</color> chance to apply <color=#FFC926>Assimilate</color> to it for 4 rounds.

While a ship is affected by the <color=#FFC926>Assimilate</color> state, Officer Abilities have their effectiveness reduced by 25%.

<color=#B8DEE5>Below-Decks Abilities are only activated when assigned to a below-decks slot on a ship</color>.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3412597742, 'officer_ability_name_51006', 'Adapt and Assimilate', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3412597742, 'officer_ability_short_desc_51006', '<color=#40FF60>{1:#,#%}</color> chance of applying <color=#FFC926>Assimilate</color> to opponents with less than 95% Hull Health each Round for 4 rounds.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
