INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2343910766, 'officer_tooltip_description_55001', '<color=#309BBF>Red Alert! Raise Shields!</color>
When you take hull damage from a non-Player hostile or Armada, Kathryn Janeway increases your Shield Mitigation by <color=#40FF60>+{0:#,#%}</color> for 1 round. (cumulative).
<i>(Weapons with multiple shots will only trigger this ability once per attack.)</i>

<i>Kathryn Janeway receives full synergy bonuses from all Voyager officers regardless of class.</i>

<color=#309BBF>Bend the Rules</color>
At the start of combat, Kathryn Janeway increases your Isolytic Cascade damage by <color=#40FF60>+{2:#,#%}</color> against non-Player hostiles and Armadas.

Isolytic Cascade multiplies your <color=#40FF60>total damage</color>, including <color=#40FF60>Isolytic Damage</color>, and all research and other bonuses.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
