INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3131537917, 'officer_tooltip_description_67001', '<color=#309BBF>Take the Shot</color>
On round start against players, Mirror Picard increases your Isolytic Cascade damage by <color=#40FF60>{0:#,#%}</color> for 2 rounds.

<color=#309BBF>Anticollective</color>
On round start against players with <color=#FFC926>Assimilate</color>, Mirror Picard increases your <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> by <color=#40FF60>{2:#}</color> for 1 round.

<color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> provides <b>true damage mitigation</b> from all sources <i>after</i> all other bonuses. Every 100 Apex Barrier increases the damage you can take by 1%.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
