INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (435759625, 'officer_tooltip_description_67002', '<color=#309BBF>Self-Improvement</color>
On combat start while against an Interceptor player, Mirror Data increases your <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> by <color=#40FF60>{0:#}</color> for the duration of combat.

<color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> provides <b>true damage mitigation</b> from all sources <i>after</i> all other bonuses. Every 100 Apex Barrier increases the damage you can take by 1%.

<color=#309BBF>Reflections</color>
On round start against players, Mirror Data has <color=#40FF60>{3:#,#%}</color> chance to apply <color=#FFC926>Assimilate</color> to them for 2 rounds.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
