INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3643810820, 'officer_tooltip_description_68004', '<color=#309BBF>Test That Assumption</color>
Lieutenant Picard increases your <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> by <color=#40FF60>{0:#}</color> vs non-Armada hostiles.<color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> provides <b>true damage mitigation</b> from all sources <i>after</i> all other bonuses. Every 100 <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> increases the damage you can take by 1%.

With full <b>Synergy</b>, Lieutenant Picard provides 11,000 <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> which reduces the incoming damage by 55%.

Works against Hostiles of level 35 and under.

This ability does not trigger when Tal is assigned to the bridge of your ship.

<color=#B8DEE5>Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship</color>.

<color=#309BBF>Always a Light</color>
<color=#40FF60>+{2:#.#%}</color> to the Shield Health', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
