INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (783581005, 'officer_tooltip_description_73001', '<color=#309BBF>Time Is the Fire...</color>
On round start against players, Soran has <color=#40FF60>{1:#,#%}</color> chance to apply <color=#FFC926>Burning</color> to your target for 1 round.

<color=#309BBF>Toothless Predator</color>
On round start against players commanding an Explorer afflicted by <color=#FFC926>Burning</color>, Soran increases your <color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> by <color=#40FF60>{2:#}</color> for 5 rounds.

<color=#6BB7FF>Apex Barrier</color> provides <b>true damage mitigation</b> from all sources <i>after</i> all other bonuses. Every 100 Apex Barrier increases the damage you can take by 1%.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
