INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (312289551, 'officer_flavor_text_73002', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> SCIENCE
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> EXPLORER RETALIATION SQUAD
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> INDEPENDENT

In the 23rd century, the Borg Collective invaded the El-Aurian homeworld. The assimilation of the El-Aurians was swift and brutal, with their culture and way of life decimated in mere moments. As millions of El-Aurians were either assimilated or killed, a small number of survivors were scattered to the stars. Following their escape from the Borg, a contingent of 415 El-Aurian refugees were traveling to Earth when their transport vessels, the SS Lakul and SS Robert Fox, became trapped in a powerful and erratic energy ribbon which acted as a doorway to an extra-dimensional realm known as the Nexus. With the destruction of the transport ships by the forces of the energy ribbon deemed an inevitability, the USS Enterprise-B launched a rescue mission, managing to rescue 47 El-Aurian refugees in the process. Romi was one of those survivors.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
