INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2458983580, 'officer_flavor_text_75002', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> SCIENCE
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> VOYAGER 30TH ANNIVERSARY
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> INDEPENDENT

How far would you go to save your own life?
Trapped thousands of light years from home and faced with a future of endless wandering of the stars, Seska made a decision. She would do what no one else aboard Voyager had the courage to do.
She would save her own life.
Seska betrayed her fellow crew members, acting as a spy for the Cardassians under the promise of an imminent return to Earth. Of course, their promise of salvation was fictitious, but desperate people are willing to believe almost anything.
Seska proved herself as a cunning, dedicated operative, successfully hiding her true intentions from her crew for some time before she was eventually exposed as a traitor.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2458983580, 'officer_name_75002', 'Seska', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
